<p class="ql-align-justify">78 Do Leaders Have Moral Obligations? 领导人是否有道德义务？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">79 Do Great Leaders Have to Be Outgoing? 伟大的领导人（或者领军人物）是否都必须外向？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">80 Do You Support or Oppose the Death Penalty? 你是否支持死刑？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Parenting and Childhood</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>为人父母和童年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">81 Should Birth Control Pills Be Available to Teenage Girls Without a Prescription? 是否应该向十几岁的女孩子提供不用医生允许就可以获得的避孕药？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">82 Is Modern Culture Ruining Childhood? 现代文化是否破坏了童年？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">83 Are Adults Hurting Young Children by Pushing Them to Achieve? 当成年人督促孩子们一定要成功的时候，是否也伤害了他们？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">84 How, and by Whom, Should Children Be Taught Appropriate Behavior? 到底应该是谁，用什么方法，来教孩子们什么才是合适的举止？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">85 What Can Older People Learn From Your Generation? 老年人可以向年轻人学习什么？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">86 Do ‘Shame and Blame’ Work to Change Teenage Behavior? “羞辱和指责”这种教育方法是否对规范青少年举止的问题上管用？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">87 How Should Children Be Taught About Puberty and Sex? 该怎么教孩子关于青春期和性的问题？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">88 Is Dating a Thing of the Past? 约会这档子事是不是过时了？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">89 How Should Parents Handle a Bad Report Card? 家长应该如何面对一份难看的成绩单？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Health and Nutrition</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>健康和营养</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">90 Are Antismoking Ads Effective? 反吸烟的广告是否管用？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">91 Is Drinking and Driving Still a Problem for Teenagers? 酒后驾车是否还是青少年的问题？（美国特色）</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">92 Is It Ethical to Eat Meat? 吃肉是否道德？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">93 Should the Government Limit the Size of Sugary Drinks? 政府是否应该限制含糖饮料的容量？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">94 Should Marijuana Be Legal? 大麻应该合法吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">Personal Character and Morality Questions</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">个人品格和道德</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">95 Should You Care About the Health and Safety of Those Making Your Clothing? 你是否应当关心那些给你做衣服的人们的健康和安全问题？（这这，这含沙射影）</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">96 Can Money Buy You Happiness? 钱能买来幸福么？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">97 Are We Losing the Art of Listening? 我们是否在遗失聆听的艺术？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">98 Do People Complain Too Much? 人们是不是吐槽太多了？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">99 Is Your Generation More Self-Centered Than Earlier Generations? 你这一代孩子是不是比前几代人更加自我中心？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">100 Should Couples Live Together Before Marriage? 情侣们是否应该婚前同居？</p>